ed="T" n="0734a11"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0734a11"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023578">中大雲寺</placeName><persName key="A001416">圓暉</persName>傳（<persName key="A021682">懷遠</persName> <persName key="A009380">崇廙</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0734a12"/><persName key="A001416">釋圓暉</persName>，未詳何許人也。<placeName key="PL000000042002">關輔</placeName>之間，聲名籍<lb
ed="T" n="0734a13"/>甚<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g691"/>，精研性相，善達諸宗。幼於《俱舍》<ptr target="#n1429"/>一門，最<lb
ed="T" n="0734a14"/>為銳意。時禮部侍郎<persName key="A009364">賈曾</persName>歸心<name>釋</name>氏<ptr target="#n712"/>，好樂<lb
ed="T" n="0734a15"/>斯文，多命<persName key="A001416">暉</persName>談此宗相。然其難者則「非想<lb
ed="T" n="0734a16"/>見惑<ptr target="#n538"/>」，繁者則〈得非得〉章<ptr target="#n714"/>。爰請<persName key="A001416">暉<roleName>師</roleName></persName>略伸梗<lb
ed="T" n="0734a17"/>概<ptr target="#n715"/>，究其<persName key="A000060">光<roleName>師</roleName></persName>疏義繁極難尋<ptr target="#n534"/>。又<placeName key="PL000000023661">聖善寺</placeName><persName key="A021682">懷遠<lb
ed="T" n="0734a18"/><roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，願心相合，因節略古疏──頌則再牒而釋，<lb
ed="T" n="0734a19"/>論乃有引而具注<ptr target="#n717"/>──，甚為徑捷，學者易知。後<lb
ed="T" n="0734a20"/>有<persName key="A009380">崇廙</persName>著《金華鈔》十卷以解焉。<persName key="A000060">光</persName>、<persName key="A000746">寶</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n718"/>二師<lb
ed="T" n="0734a21"/>之後，<persName key="A001416">暉<roleName>公</roleName></persName>間出，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000001520 #PL000000005198">兩河</ref>間、<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042190 #PL000000023583">二京道</ref>、<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000020249">齊</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000010514">楚</placeName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0734a22"/><placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>盛行<persName key="A001416">暉</persName>疏焉。</p>
